16
00:01:17,433 --> 00:01:21,676
[SPEAKER_01]: And the way that we do that is by generating something called a space summary.

17
00:01:21,696 --> 00:01:28,940
[SPEAKER_01]: The space summary is an itemized list, an inventory of every single occupied space that can be found within the new high school building.

18
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:34,443
[SPEAKER_01]: We're planning for both what is here at the high school today as well as projecting forward.

19
00:01:34,803 --> 00:01:41,007
