20
00:01:41,247 --> 00:01:51,533
[SPEAKER_01]: The space summary includes both occupied spaces as well as unoccupied spaces, things like stairs, hallways, mechanical rooms, everything that is needed to support the building.

21
00:01:51,633 --> 00:01:56,276
[SPEAKER_01]: And when we combine both the occupied spaces and the non-occupied spaces, that gives us the overall building size.

22
